column2: SELECT P.SpecObjID as objid_P, S.SpecObjID as objid_S,   P.subclass as class_P, S.subclass as class_S,   P.ra as ra_P, P.dec as dec_P, S.ra as ra_S, S.dec as dec_S,   P.z as z_P, S.z as z_S,   N.distance into mydb.NearbyGal_SandTest from SpecPhotoAll P			     JOIN Neighbors N ON P.ObjID = N.ObjID     JOIN	SpecPhotoAll S ON S.ObjID = N.NeighborObjID   WHERE    P.ObjID < S.ObjID                        and P.class = &&& and (P.subclass = &&& or P.subclass = &&&)      and S.class = &&& and (S.subclass = &&& or S.subclass = &&&)      and (     ((#+P.z)*# < (#+S.z)*# and (#+P.z)*# > (#+S.z)*#)       or     ((#+P.z)*# < (#+S.z)*# and (#+P.z)*# > (#+S.z)*#)       or     ((#+P.z)*# < (#+S.z)*# and (#+P.z)*# > (#+S.z)*#)       or     ((#+P.z)*# < (#+S.z)*# and (#+P.z)*# > (#+S.z)*#)       or     ((#+P.z)*# < (#+S.z)*# and (#+P.z)*# > (#+S.z)*#)     )
